{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who was the scapegoat?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish people were the scapegoat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the end of the congress towards evening, the hooligans let loose in the city, smashed windows, looted houses, beat up people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the first taste for me of what we were going to face if fascism ever got hold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a mini pogrom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think there were any people killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were a lot of-- in our particular house, I remember we had a house that was facing the-- the front, the main street and the side street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The rocks that were thrown into our house ended up in the kitchen, which came from both sides.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when this was over, there was glass all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a Kristallnacht in our own house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it was in '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was either '38 or '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a year or two before-- before the-- the war really started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in the summertime-- late summer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was late summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Shortly after that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on a given day, I remember the Soviet Union gave an ultimatum to Romania to-- that Romania should evacuate or leave the two provinces-- the two northern provinces bordering on the Soviet Union-- the Bukovina and Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We didn't know whether Romania was going to go to war or whether they were going to give up peacefully.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Romania--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians gave them 24 hours or 36 hours to reply.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were very naive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I remember in circumstances like that, had we had more experience, we would have been-- we would have been in hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or, we would have trying to seek shelter.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
